            "titleSlug": "diamond-pattern_798",
            "content": "<h4 id=\"print-the-following-pattern-for-the-given-number-of-rows\">Print the following pattern for the given number of rows.</h4>\n\n<h5 id=\"note-n-is-always-odd\">Note: N is always odd.</h5>\n\n<p><br></p>\n\n<h5 id=\"pattern-for-n-5\">Pattern for N = 5</h5>\n\n<p><br>\n<img src=\"https://ninjasfiles.s3.amazonaws.com/0000000000003726.png\" height=\"81\" width=\"43\" /></p>\n\n<h4 id=\"the-dots-represent-spaces\">The dots represent spaces.</h4>\n\n<p><br>\n<br></p>\n\n<h5 id=\"input-format\">Input format :</h5>\n\n<pre><code>N (Total no. of rows and can only be odd)\n</code></pre>\n\n<h5 id=\"output-format\">Output format :</h5>\n\n<pre><code>Pattern in N lines\n</code></pre>\n\n<h5 id=\"constraints\">Constraints :</h5>\n\n<pre><code>1 &lt;= N &lt;= 49\n</code></pre>\n<h5 id=\"sample-input-1\">Sample Input 1:</h5>\n\n<pre><code>5\n</code></pre>\n\n<h5 id=\"sample-output-1\">Sample Output 1:</h5>\n\n<pre><code>  *\n ***\n*****\n ***\n  *\n</code></pre>\n\n<h5 id=\"sample-input-2\">Sample Input 2:</h5>\n\n<pre><code>3\n</code></pre>\n\n<h5 id=\"sample-output-2\">Sample Output 2:</h5>\n\n<pre><code>  *\n ***\n  *\n</code></pre>\n",
